            <title><![CDATA[【[话筒]警惕！#经常熬夜久坐患糖尿病几率大#】目前，我国成年人糖尿病患病率总体呈升高趋势，其中，2型糖尿病患者占90%以上，#绝大多数糖尿病尚无彻底治愈办法#...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>警惕！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%BB%8F%E5%B8%B8%E7%86%AC%E5%A4%9C%E4%B9%85%E5%9D%90%E6%82%A3%E7%B3%96%E5%B0%BF%E7%97%85%E5%87%A0%E7%8E%87%E5%A4%A7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%BB%8F%E5%B8%B8%E7%86%AC%E5%A4%9C%E4%B9%85%E5%9D%90%E6%82%A3%E7%B3%96%E5%B0%BF%E7%97%85%E5%87%A0%E7%8E%87%E5%A4%A7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#经常熬夜久坐患糖尿病几率大#</span></a>】目前，我国成年人糖尿病患病率总体呈升高趋势，其中，2型糖尿病患者占90%以上，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%BB%9D%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%9A%E6%95%B0%E7%B3%96%E5%B0%BF%E7%97%85%E5%B0%9A%E6%97%A0%E5%BD%BB%E5%BA%95%E6%B2%BB%E6%84%88%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%BB%9D%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%9A%E6%95%B0%E7%B3%96%E5%B0%BF%E7%97%85%E5%B0%9A%E6%97%A0%E5%BD%BB%E5%BA%95%E6%B2%BB%E6%84%88%E5%8A%9E%E6%B3%95%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#绝大多数糖尿病尚无彻底治愈办法#</span></a>。哪种信号提示你已经被糖尿病“盯上”👀？今天，联合国<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%B3%96%E5%B0%BF%E7%97%85%E6%97%A5%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#糖尿病日#</span></a>，戳图学习👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a> <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%A0%E5%85%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87v%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%A0%E5%85%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87v%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#健康素养提升v计划#</span></a> （央视新闻） <img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hjuf3ka50cj20u06nge81.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br>